Module org.nasdanika.resources
Package org.nasdanika.resources

Class BinaryContainerImpl

java.lang.Object
org.nasdanika.resources.BinaryContainerImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
BinaryContainer, Container<InputStream>, Resource<InputStream>
public class BinaryContainerImpl extends Object implements BinaryContainer
Delegates all calls to the target. Wraps return types of getContainer() and getParent() into BinaryContainerImpl.
Author:
Pavel
